thread.title: BRIEF-National Storage Affiliates Trust Q4 Core FFO Per Share $0.32

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-National Storage Affiliates Trust Q4 Core FFO Per Share $0.32
text:
Feb 26 (Reuters) - National Storage Affiliates Trust :
* REPORTS FOURTH QUARTER AND FULL YEAR 2017 RESULTS * Q4 SAME STORE SALES ROSE 5 PERCENT * Q4 CORE FFO PER SHARE $0.32 * SEES 2018 CORE FFO PER SHARE $1.33 TO $1.37 * SEES 2018 SAME STORE OPERATIONS NOI GROWTH OF 4.0% TO 5.5%
* Q4 FFO PER SHARE VIEW $0.32 -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* FY2018 FFO PER SHARE VIEW $1.35 -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* QTRLY FFO PER SHARE AND UNIT $0.31 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
